{
  "stem": "1216.3",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And that fifth grade went from, oh, about 11-year-olds all the way up to 16-year-olds, because people had been in camps, they had been in hiding, they had been in Germany and work camps, various other reasons.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So everybody was in a mess.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And that situation lasted all the way through high school.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "1959.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "February 4, 1959.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "How?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Well, I came, actually, on what was supposed to be a visit.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I had had a job in Holland as a translator/proofreader for a medical journal, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] and quit the job, went to England, where by then my parents lived, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] couldn't find a job there, even if only because I didn't have the nationality.",
      "word_count": 49
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] So between my parents and me, we decided maybe I should go to secretarial school.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I am profoundly grateful I never did.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But anyway, that's what we decided.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And that didn't start right away, so my parents decided to send me to the United States for three or four months to friends of ours to see how life was lived here.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And that's what we did, except then I decided I wanted to stay.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And the one and only time that my German birth has made something good happen to me was then, because it was still a quota system.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "The Dutch quota was pretty well full.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "The German quota was wide open.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I didn't even have to go home, or go to Canada, or whatever to get my first papers.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I could stay right were I was.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
